         <abstract id="aspace_61210f0034a027c638ff6460d90a9b28">Kingman Brewster, Jr., was inaugurated the seventeenth president of Yale University on 11 April 1964. The records document the planning and management of the inauguration and include press materials, such as clippings, releases, and the Yale Daily News special inauguration edition; invitations, tickets, and the ceremony program; congratulation messages; invitation and attendance lists; and records detailing ceremonial order and logistics. The records also include congratulation messages on Brewster's appointment as Yale University Provost in 1959.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <corpname source="local">
               <part>Yale University. President's Office</part>
            </corpname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_991aa37c05fd679eceb39ccc0beab512">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 2-A (YRG 2-A), Records of the President.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_4f18145938cb72c5f98dfc03eef8bd00">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Office of the President, 1976 and 1978.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_155c7f323082049d2e0679c850796edf">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_06da30e70d1cc54f546439f758ca6e6c">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Kingman Brewster, Jr., President of Yale University, Inauguration Records (RU 13). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_547867b7dd0f127eb135a202b00ecb83">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_da5578ed6cfb92c79c921458959056c0">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Kingman Brewster, Jr., was inaugurated the seventeenth president of Yale University on 11 April 1964. The records document the planning and management of the inauguration and include press materials, such as clippings, releases, and the Yale Daily News special inauguration edition; invitations, tickets, and the ceremony program; congratulation messages; invitation and attendance lists; and records detailing ceremonial order and logistics. The records also include congratulation messages on Brewster's appointment as Yale University Provost in 1959.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
  
